===Noun===
'''mould''' (American English spelling: '''mold''')

#loose [[friable]] [[soil]], rich in [[humus]] and fit for [[plant]]ing
====Etymology====
Old English ''molde''
====Translations====
*Latin [[humus#Latin|humus]]
